<br>
Udal<br>
Priest of Hate <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/umomur.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Momur</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Contributing Member</span><br>  Posts: 315<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(6/5/02 3:20:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=104.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about factions</span><hr size=1> There are always people around.  There are no hostile mobs (or any mobs) between Nexus-Bazaar-Shadowhaven. <br>
<br>
Paludal Caverns, off of SH, offers SICK amounts of exp for leveling from 15 to low 20s super fast.  You can easily ding every 2-4 hours. Loot is pretty good (if you are untwinked) and sells for ok cash.<br>
<br>
Neth Lair and Marus Seru (DL Junior) are populated with people willing to group up til about 20.  Neth Lair offers little loot.  Marus Seru loot sucks.<br>
<br>
