<br>
The best way to work Seru Faction is to level in Marus seru killing Recusos or to Level in Mons Let killing Thought leeches (TLs are better faction wise)<br>
<br>
The best way to work Katta faction is to kill Coterie.  Neither of these faction techs lower the opposing cities faction.<br>
<br>
but Coterie and Recuso will add you to their hate list.<br>
